#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:61
msgid "Initialization List Policies"
msgstr "初始化列表策略"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:63
msgid ""
"The asbind20 provides some policies for adapting existing C++ paradigm "
"for constructing from a range of value."
msgstr ""
"asbind20 提供了一些策略用于适配现有的 C++ 构造模式，"
"以便从值的范围进行构造。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:66
msgid "List Pattern with Limited Elements"
msgstr "有限元素的列表模式"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:68
msgid ""
"Policies for the pattern with limited elements, i.e., no ``repeat`` in "
"the pattern."
msgstr "针对有限元素模式的策略，即模式中没有 ``repeat``。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:70
msgid "Applying"
msgstr "应用"

