#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:90
msgid "List Pattern with Repeated Elements"
msgstr "重复元素的列表模式"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:92
msgid ""
"Policies for the pattern with repeated elements, i.e., containing "
"``repeat`` in the pattern."
msgstr "针对重复元素模式的策略，即模式中包含 ``repeat``。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:94
msgid "Automatically convert to ``script_init_list_repeat``"
msgstr "自动转换为 ``script_init_list_repeat``"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:115
msgid "As an iterator pair of ``[begin, end)``"
msgstr "作为迭代器对 ``[begin, end)``"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:138
msgid "As a pair of pointer and size"
msgstr "作为指针和大小对"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:158
msgid "As the ``std::initializer_list``"
msgstr "作为 ``std::initializer_list``"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:179
msgid ""
"This policy is implemented by non-standard code, please check the macro "
"``ASBIND20_HAS_AS_INITIALIZER_LIST`` at first."
msgstr ""
"此策略由非标准代码实现，请首先检查宏 ``ASBIND20_HAS_AS_INITIALIZER_LIST``。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:181
msgid "Currently, this policy are supported on MSVC STL, libstdc++, and libc++."
msgstr "目前，此策略在 MSVC STL、libstdc++ 和 libc++ 上受支持。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:183
msgid "As the ``std::span``"
msgstr "作为 ``std::span``"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:203
msgid "``std::from_range`` and a range"
msgstr "``std::from_range`` 和范围"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:225
msgid ""
"This policy is only available when compiler supports C++23. You can check"
" whether the macro ``ASBIND20_HAS_CONTAINERS_RANGES`` is defined."
msgstr ""
"此策略仅在编译器支持 C++23 时可用。"
"你可以检查宏 ``ASBIND20_HAS_CONTAINERS_RANGES`` 是否已定义。"

